<section id="journey" class="narrative-journey">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">The Journey to Mental Clarity</h2>
    
    <div class="journey-steps">
      <div class="journey-step" id="step1">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <div class="fog-icon"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>The Fog</h3>
          <p>Many of us experience life through a mental fog – anxiety, stress, and uncertainty cloud our decisions and drain our energy. You may feel stuck, overwhelmed, or disconnected from your true purpose.</p>
          <p>When clarity is missing, even small decisions become exhausting. The mental fog affects your relationships, career, and most importantly, your relationship with yourself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="journey-connector"></div>
      
      <div class="journey-step" id="step2">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <div class="shift-icon"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>The Shift</h3>
          <p>Transformation begins with awareness. The first step toward clarity is recognizing that your thoughts create your experience, and that mental wellness is a skill that can be developed.</p>
          <p>Through the Visio Relief system, you'll experience a profound shift in perspective. You'll learn to separate yourself from anxious thoughts and reconnect with your inner wisdom.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="journey-connector"></div>
      
      <div class="journey-step" id="step3">
        <div class="step-icon">
          <div class="vision-icon"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>The Vision</h3>
          <p>With a clear mind comes clear vision. You'll develop the ability to see opportunities you once missed, make decisions with confidence, and experience deeper connections in all areas of your life.</p>
          <p>Mental clarity isn't just about reducing stress – it's about creating space for joy, purpose, and authentic self-expression. It's about living a life that feels aligned with your truest self.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Simple intersection observer for fade-in effect
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.2 });
    
    const steps = document.querySelectorAll('.journey-step');
    steps.forEach(step => observer.observe(step));
  });
</script>

